<p style="Normal">Build fix.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixes to Win32 Insert Symbol dialog.</p>
<p style="Normal">More fixes to Win32 keyboard handling.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes: 338, 2481</p>
