<p style="Normal">Image drag-n-drop.</p>
<p style="Normal">Relocated an ifdef which was breaking non-debug builds.</p>
<p style="Normal">Images can be resized by dragging handles on the screen.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed aspect ratio problem when resizing images.</p>
<p style="Normal">Left click selects an image now.</p>
<p style="Normal">Build fix on unix.</p>
