<p style="Normal">Fixes for caret, and other display issues, such as page number display during document load and size of scrollbars.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed table cells to expand immediately when text pasted in.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed caret disappearance after selecting and deleting text.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed a bug with images not resizing on zoom.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed an evil race crash.</p>
<p style="Normal">Made tables display immediately after work on them.</p>
<p style="Normal">Made lines in tables not disappear when text is selected.</p>
<p style="Normal">Drag table lines with the mouse.</p>
<p style="Normal">Lots of bug fixes.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added autoformat of table lines on double-click.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed a memory bug.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed unix printing.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Daniel Yacob</p>
<p style="Normal">Amharic localisation work.</p>
